{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2013, "height": 2762, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十九世杜位高：大专。", "block_bbox": [182, 228, 573, 283], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "南张村：", "block_bbox": [180, 298, 341, 351], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十世杜若甫：字友白，敦族谊，助乡里，倡修祠堂，编修家谱，事迹详见录于《渑池县志》之《杜友白传》。\n", "block_bbox": [176, 367, 1677, 495], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一世杜焕章：若福次子，庠生。", "block_bbox": [180, 509, 768, 566], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一世杜含章：若福四子，举人，公字子贞，号绍峰先生，乾隆乙卯科房元，即乾隆六十年（1795)举人，其为人，孝友醇实，笃嗜读书。其为文，宏深雅健，雄视一世。又熟于《天文志》《地理图》《律吕精义》《皇极经世》诸书，所著《易经句解》《书经句解》《四书述要》等，例授文林郎，曾补考城县训导。与其子事迹详《清例授文林郎借补考城县训导绍峰杜老先生父子懿德碑》。\n", "block_bbox": [175, 580, 1679, 913], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十二世杜文琳：含章长子。庠生，公弱冠游庠，克承家学，天性醇谨，循循善诱，启迪之广，几于老先生声望相等。\n", "block_bbox": [176, 929, 1677, 1052], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜云：在国家公安部工作。", "block_bbox": [181, 1068, 791, 1125], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜平：在国家航空部工作。", "block_bbox": [182, 1139, 792, 1194], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜华：在中央军委政治部做宣传工作。", "block_bbox": [182, 1209, 1002, 1264], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜金伟：郑州市委党校校长。", "block_bbox": [181, 1279, 836, 1333], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜娟：女，清华大学教授。", "block_bbox": [182, 1348, 771, 1404], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜作哲：曾在私垫任教。", "block_bbox": [181, 1418, 753, 1472], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十六世杜永曾：曾任八路军太岳军区独七旅连长。", "block_bbox": [181, 1485, 1088, 1540], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十六世杜敏曾：义马市教育局会计。平生至孝，又敦族谊，1962年被划为右派，仍一力与修家谱。1988年复参与修谱。\n", "block_bbox": [177, 1555, 1681, 1681], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜铭心：义马市千秋中小学校长。", "block_bbox": [179, 1695, 924, 1750], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜克治：敏曾子，大专学历，小学高级教师。", "block_bbox": [181, 1766, 1091, 1822], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜彩霞：敏曾女，大专学历，小学高级教师。", "block_bbox": [181, 1837, 1093, 1893], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜海平：铭心子，小学高级教师。", "block_bbox": [183, 1908, 906, 1963], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜瑞平：铭心女，大专学历，义马市教育局人事科、财务科长。", "block_bbox": [181, 1978, 1411, 2036], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜晓怡：女，大学法律系毕业。", "block_bbox": [180, 2051, 867, 2107], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜娟：大专学历。", "block_bbox": [180, 2122, 628, 2177], "block_id": 20, "block_order": 21}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜海云：曾任小学教师。", "block_bbox": [178, 2194, 757, 2249], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 22}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十九世杜琳：本科学历，中教二级教师。", "block_bbox": [179, 2265, 909, 2320], "block_id": 22, "block_order": 23}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十九世杜星辉：大专学历。", "block_bbox": [180, 2334, 672, 2389], "block_id": 23, "block_order": 24}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十二世杜万贵：经营粮油生意起家，田产甚丰。", "block_bbox": [178, 2474, 1033, 2531], "block_id": 24, "block_order": 25}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1795, 719, 1874, 1430], "block_id": 25, "block_order": 26}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三二四", "block_bbox": [1809, 2084, 1863, 2207], "block_id": 26, "block_order": 27}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6207729578018188, "coordinate": [175.06610107421875, 580.1680908203125, 1679.725830078125, 913.9393310546875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5760570168495178, "coordinate": [177.32000732421875, 1555.92919921875, 1681.256591796875, 1681.28857421875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5607447028160095, "coordinate": [176.95050048828125, 367.48187255859375, 1677.395751953125, 495.57232666015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5417339205741882, "coordinate": [176.85015869140625, 929.3558349609375, 1677.733154296875, 1052.7215576171875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5181345343589783, "coordinate": [181.41217041015625, 1978.51513671875, 1411.6650390625, 2036.2294921875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5180237889289856, "coordinate": [178.77978515625, 2474.2802734375, 1033.0631103515625, 2531.4384765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.49296626448631287, "coordinate": [181.40182495117188, 1766.127685546875, 1091.968505859375, 1822.194580078125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.4867633581161499, "coordinate": [180.2474365234375, 2051.5791015625, 867.6461181640625, 2107.5966796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.4850684702396393, "coordinate": [179.547119140625, 1695.9879150390625, 924.0703125, 1750.2081298828125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.48060330748558044, "coordinate": [183.39944458007812, 1908.89501953125, 906.5880126953125, 1963.9345703125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.4805503487586975, "coord